123
00:06:13,988 --> 00:06:18,676
Typically, an armed military submarine 
consists of three levels or decks.

124
00:06:18,676 --> 00:06:21,957
This video will mostly focus on military submarines,

125
00:06:21,957 --> 00:06:26,463
as they constitute the majority of submarines worldwide.

126
00:06:26,463 --> 00:06:30,105
It's worth noting that the designs of 
research and tourism submarines may differ.

127
