262
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:41,933
Moving to the category of nuclear submarines,

263
00:13:41,933 --> 00:13:44,829
India has named its class Arihant,

264
00:13:45,212 --> 00:13:49,253
Currently, there are two active nuclear submarines in this class,

265
00:13:49,253 --> 00:13:52,383
with two more under construction in Vishakhapatnam.

266
00:13:52,383 --> 00:13:55,772
The Arihant-class submarines have the 
capability to carry ballistic missiles,

267
00:13:55,772 --> 00:13:58,511
Ballistic missiles are self-guided missiles

268
00:13:58,511 --> 00:14:00,658
