272
00:14:14,818 --> 00:14:17,111
Talking about the other developed countries,

273
00:14:17,111 --> 00:14:19,764
the American Navy's Ohio-class submarines

274
00:14:19,764 --> 00:14:22,549
are considered among the most powerful in the world.

275
00:14:22,549 --> 00:14:25,463
The U.S. possesses a total of 18 Ohio-class submarines,

276
00:14:25,463 --> 00:14:31,434
