277
00:14:31,434 --> 00:14:37,373
Furthermore, each Trident 2 missile can 
potentially accommodate 14 nuclear bombs.

278
00:14:37,373 --> 00:14:39,175
When the United States and Russia

279
00:14:39,175 --> 00:14:42,358
