280
00:14:42,358 --> 00:14:44,452
they entered into the START 1 agreement.

281
00:14:44,452 --> 00:14:48,982
The terms of the agreement specified 
a reduction limit from 14 to 8.

282
00:14:48,982 --> 00:14:51,914
This START I treaty, officially known 
as the Strategic Arms Reduction Treaty,

283
00:14:51,914 --> 00:14:54,867
was the first treaty between the U.S. and the Soviet Union

284
00:14:54,867 --> 00:14:57,353
to reduce strategic nuclear weapons.

285
00:14:57,506 --> 00:15:01,147
Beyond these, the U.S. Navy features other submarine classes,

286
00:15:01,147 --> 00:15:04,633
such as Los Angeles, Columbia, and Virginia classes.

287
00:15:04,633 --> 00:15:10,267
In Russia, the Yasen class stands out as the 
most powerful nuclear attack submarine.

288
00:15:10,267 --> 00:15:12,784
Besides India, Russia, and the U.S., other countries like

289
00:15:12,784 --> 00:15:17,323
China, the UK, France, and Germany 
